humanMachineDialogue.author: Memory Reasoning
humanMachineDialogue.text: The report states 'Lymph node status: Negative 0/2.' This means that out of the two sentinel lymph nodes examined, neither contained metastases. This is consistent with the N0 stage, which indicates no metastatic carcinoma in regional lymph nodes. The new rules 10 and 11 support this conclusion.

humanMachineDialogue.text: The pathology report states 'Lymph nodes: Sentinel lymph node. Lymph node status: Negative 0/2.' This means that out of the 2 sentinel lymph nodes examined, no metastases were found. Therefore, the N stage for this patient is N0.
